{"tid":163870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"崔順實女兒鄭尤拉代表律師無故猝死","createTime":"2017-03-20T09:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T11:07:02.000Z","uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7745ef1bfaa49c56aa4e457c5fb62715087b686","tid":163870,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:49:59.000Z","msg":"南韓前總統朴槿惠涉嫌讓親信崔順實干政與收賄，遭到彈劾下台，丹麥於今年1月逮捕此案重要嫌犯、崔順實之女鄭尤拉後，近日同意將她引渡回國，但鄭尤拉的律師林肯柏格（Peter Martin Blinkenberg）卻在17日不明原因猝死，引發許多揣測。<br />\n<br />\n據《韓國時報》報導，林肯柏格之死讓外界懷疑有可能是暗殺，以防止鄭尤拉上訴成功後繼續留在丹麥。林肯柏格過去曾擔任過經濟犯罪類的首席檢察官，轉任律師後幫助許多客戶無罪釋放。<br />\n<br />\n丹麥記者伯恩森（Markus Bernsen）透露，鄭尤拉律師之死不會對案情有太多影響，因為她會再獲得一個新的律師，該名律師依舊會提出上訴反對引渡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yaxo1fgm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyaxo1fgm&h=3ffb1436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e397f183d8ad4e35a2384552a212ba0030eb3abe","tid":163870,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d843b8968f53f4848a3e2c6449e9247eb8c03b","tid":163870,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2010280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2010280&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4741686a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2010280&h=80696442\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2010280</a>"},{"pid":"936ee154ee64528d72b7260a4e808e8931c30cca","tid":163870,"uid":41